{"tid":513493,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(急求醫學JJ入) 保濟丸同撲熱息痛可以一齊食?","createTime":"2017-12-29T14:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T08:18:31.000Z","uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b737c21d226790111da7365644eb9cf2d5a4f0ba","tid":513493,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"依家疑似腸胃炎 好辛苦 附近又無醫生睇<br />\n所以2個鐘前食咗一樽保濟丸 (正常食兩樽)<br />\n但係依家開始發燒頭暈頭痛<br />\n有無巴打知依家食必理痛(撲熱息痛)會唔會出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有熱心巴打解答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3cd7c39cba00028d2cd8ef4efd29c6676434ac","tid":513493,"uid":27261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"會狂賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31c99811360aedff2993811dfc532b5ee10a365","tid":513493,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"梗係唔好"},{"pid":"0e8f0a5377c4712e7c35ec3f4ea8f4c24235ad12","tid":513493,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3cd7c39cba00028d2cd8ef4efd29c6676434ac","tid":513493,"uid":27261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"會狂賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"係咁疴屎所以先食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fc2d497a75ad86bb78b8a0381a9db23a9c39eb","tid":513493,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"探完熱 依家燒到38.5度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372eec2934cedef17d5